# ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  ARCHON-IX | .GITIGNORE PROTOCOL                        ║
# ║  Purpose: Boundary Definition & Asset Isolation          ║
# ║  Directive: Protect the estate; exclude entropy.         ║
# ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# 🛡️ 1. SOVEREIGN SECRETS (Critical)
# Prevents exposure of API keys, database credentials, and private keys.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.pem
keys.json
config/credentials.json

# 📦 2. DEPENDENCY ENTROPY
# Excludes massive dependency folders managed by package managers.
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# 🏗️ 3. BUILD ARTIFACTS (The Square of Objective Reality)
# Source code is the truth; compiled files are disposable.
dist/
build/
.vite/
out/
.nuxt/
.next/

# 💻 4. EDITOR & SYSTEM CLUTTER
# Protects the repository from local machine noise.
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# 🦋 5. FLUTTER & SUPABASE SILOS (Codex Alignment)
# Specific exclusions for the technical architecture modules.

# Flutter
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.packages
.build/

# Supabase
supabase/.branches
supabase/.temp

#  6. THE SHADOW APPENDIX (Proprietary Logs)
# Ensure Ghost Protocol trackers and raw data dumps remain local until sanitized.
*.csv (Optional: Uncomment if you store raw Ghost logs locally)
logs/
audit-trail.json
